Privacy Policy – Solarus Electrical Installations Inc.

Solarus Electrical Installations Inc. values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you communicate with us through Facebook Messenger.

Information We Collect
When you message us on Facebook Messenger, we may receive your name, profile information, and message content in order to respond to your inquiries about solar power systems and related services.

How We Use Your Information
Information is used solely to:

Respond to inquiries

Provide solar-related information and support

Improve customer communication

We do not sell or share your information with third parties.

Data Storage and Retention
Messages may be stored securely for customer service and record-keeping purposes. Data is retained only as long as necessary.

Third-Party Platforms
Our messaging service uses Facebook Messenger, a platform operated by Meta Platforms, Inc. Use of Messenger is subject to Facebook’s Privacy Policy.

Your Consent
By messaging our Facebook Page, you consent to this Privacy Policy.

